Expose available query filters

Source: R/helpers.R
make_base_end_pt.Rd

Expose available query filters which are allowed to be parsed either via argument summary or filters in aims_data

make_base_end_pt(doi, aims_version = NA)

Arguments

doi

A Digital Object Identifier for a chosen AIMS data series

aims_version

A character string defining the version of database. Must be "/v1.0" or "-v2.0". If none is provided, then "-v2.0" (the most recent) is used.

Author

AIMS Datacentre adc@aims.gov.au

Contents

Developed by Diego R. Barneche, AIMS Datacentre, Greg Coleman, Duncan Fermor, Eduardo Klein, Tobias Robinson, Jason Smith, Jeffrey L. Sheehan, Shannon Dowley, Dean Ditton, Kevin Gunn, Gavin Ericson, Murray Logan, Mark Rehbein.
